Content: # Old ideas store A collection of **OLD** money-making ideas. You may not make money directly from these ideas, but I hope it will inspire you. 一个 **老** 的赚钱思路的合集。你可能不能直接从这些创意中赚钱，但是我希望能对你有所启发。 # Copyright statement All the materials are collected from the internet and contributed by netizens, which are edited accordingly and published by old-ideas-store repo. I'm not responsible for its authenticity, If there is a copyright problem, please contact the author to delete it. 版权声明 所有素材均来自网络收集以及网友投稿，由 old-ideas-store 整理发布。不对其真实性负责，若存在版权问题，请联系作者删除或添加来源声明。 # 最近在搞 AI 相关的产品，AI 时代下有没有什么机会，大家来探讨一下。 https://github.com/CrossLee/Old-ideas-store/issues/1 # Ideas list - [月入 2 W 的支付副业实践，产品迭代带来的 10 倍增长](https://github.com/CrossLee/Old-ideas-store/wiki/%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A5-2-W-%E7%9A%84%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E8%BF%AD%E4%BB%A3%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84-10-%E5%80%8D%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%BF) - [偷懒的视频搬运](https://github.com/CrossLee/Old-ideas-store/wiki/%E5%81%B7%E6%87%92%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E6%90%AC%E8%BF%90) - [月入 3k ~ 4k 的微信支付副业实践](https://github.com/CrossLee/Old-ideas-store/wiki/%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A5-3k-~-4k-%E7%9A%84%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5) - [月入 4600 的游戏网站](https://github.com/CrossLee/Old-ideas-store/wiki/%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A5-4600-%E7%9A%84%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99) - [从开源到订阅，月入 98K RMB](https://github.com/CrossLee/Old-ideas-store/wiki/%E4%BB%8E%E5%BC%80%E6%BA%90%E5%88%B0%E8%AE%A2%E9%98%85%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A5-98K-RMB) - [无人机的佣金](https://github.com/CrossLee/old-ideas-store/wiki/%E6%97%A0%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%A3%E9%87%91) - [土豆的差价](https://github.com/CrossLee/old-ideas-store/wiki/%E5%9C%9F%E8%B1%86%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%AE%E4%BB%B7) - [指纹机器](https://github.com/CrossLee/old-ideas-store/wiki/%E6%8C%87%E7%BA%B9%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8) - [储值卡的秘密](https://github.com/CrossLee/old-ideas-store/wiki/%E5%82%A8%E5%80%BC%E5%8D%A1%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86) # How to contribute Welcome to pull requests. 1. Fork this repo. 2. Create a page at wiki panel. 3. Update README.md with your wiki page link. 4. Create pull request. 欢迎提交 PR。

Vamos a discutirlo. https://github.com/CrossLee/Old-ideas-store/issues/1 # Lista de ideas - [Práctica de negocio secundario de pagos con ingresos mensuales de 20,000, crecimiento de 10 veces gracias a la iteración del producto](https://github.com/CrossLee/Old-ideas-store/wiki/%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A5-2-W-%E7%9A%84%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E8%BF%AD%E4%BB%A3%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84-10-%E5%80%8D%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%BF) - [Reutilización perezosa de videos](https://github.com/CrossLee/Old-ideas-store/wiki/%E5%81%B7%E6%87%92%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E6%90%AC%E8%BF%90) - [Práctica de negocio secundario de pagos con WeChat con ingresos mensuales de 3,000 a 4,000](https://github.com/CrossLee/Old-ideas-store/wiki/%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A5-3k-~-4k-%E7%9A%84%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5) - [Sitio web de juegos con ingresos mensuales de 4,600](https://github.com/CrossLee/Old-ideas-store/wiki/%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A5-4600-%E7%9A%84%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99) - [De open source a suscripción, ingresos mensuales de 98,000 RMB](https://github.com/CrossLee/Old-ideas-store/wiki/%E4%BB%8E%E5%BC%80%E6%BA%90%E5%88%B0%E8%AE%A2%E9%98%85%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A5-98K-RMB) - [Comisiones de drones](https://github.com/CrossLee/old-ideas-store/wiki/%E6%97%A0%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%A3%E9%87%91) - [Diferencia de precio de las patatas](https://github.com/CrossLee/old-ideas-store/wiki/%E5%9C%9F%E8%B1%86%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%AE%E4%BB%B7) - [Máquina de huellas digitales](https://github.com/CrossLee/old-ideas-store/wiki/%E6%8C%87%E7%BA%B9%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8) - [El secreto de las tarjetas de prepago](https://github.com/CrossLee/old-ideas-store/wiki/%E5%82%A8%E5%80%BC%E5%8D%A1%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86) # Cómo contribuir Bienvenido a enviar pull requests. 1. Haz fork de este repositorio. 2. Crea una página en el panel de wiki. 3. Actualiza README.md con el enlace a tu página wiki. 4. Crea un pull request. Bienvenido a enviar PR.

Content:
1. Fork 一份 Repo 到你的 GitHub 账号。
2. 在 Wiki 页签创建一个 page。
3. 修改 README.md 里按照格式添加一个链接到第 2 步创建的页面。
4. 提交 PR。
Translation:
1. Haz un Fork de un Repo a tu cuenta de GitHub.  
2. Crea una página en la pestaña Wiki.  
3. Modifica el README.md para añadir un enlace al página creada en el paso 2 siguiendo el formato.  
4. Envía un PR.
